headline: Cisco & JP Morgan to Host Innovation Tech Talk
summary: Cisco (NASDAQ: CSCO) will host a Tech Talk to discuss innovation at Cisco. The session will be led by Jeetu Patel, President and Chief Product Officer, and DJ Sampath, SVP, AI Software and Platform. Interested parties can find more information on Cisco's Investor Relations website at investor.cisco.com
